    "Containing 723 Chinese test samples, the MCTS dataset is the most extensive and widely cited evaluation dataset for tasks related to simplifying Chinese text.",
    "Originating from complex structures extracted from news corpora, each original sentence corresponds to multiple manually simplified versions.",
    "The main focus is on evaluating the understanding and rewriting capabilities of LLMs when dealing with intricate Chinese texts.",
